description: The fringe group that scrambled to subvert Trump’s 2020 loss has spent years preparing online to contest this year’s vote. This time, the world’s richest man is on their side.
title: Election deniers were aimless. Now, with Musk’s help, they’re an army.

description: If you can’t find time to meditate, or even put your phone down for more than 10 minutes, there are still ways to dissociate during the most stressful days of the year. Here are our tech recommendations to keep calm and carry on.
title: Make election week less stressful, without putting down your phone
